Description:
We had a fantastic time at the ATU Career Fair this week! It was truly inspiring to meet so many bright and ambitious students eager to kick-start their careers. 💚💛

A huge shoutout to @atucareers for organizing such a successful event! Your hard work and dedication continue to create valuable opportunities for students to connect with industry professionals and explore career possibilities. 🎉👏

Account name: ATU LeMoyne Smith School of Business
Description:
Apply to be a member of the Business Student Leadership Council today using the link in our bio 💛💚 The deadline to apply is September 16th. 

The BSLC is a prestigious organization that offers students an opportunity to serve as a student leader and ambassador for the College of Business and Economic Development.

In addition to serving as an advisor to the dean, BSLC members will be charged with recommending and developing programs and activities for the College of Business and Economic Development.

#ATUBusiness #HeckYeahTechYeah #StudentOpportunities #CollegeLife

Account name: ATU LeMoyne Smith School of Business
Description:
Congratulations to Allie for winning Cash Cow’s first giveaway of the semester!! She took home $50 of Business Bucks 💸

What’s a Business Buck?

Business Bucks are a way for students taking School of Business courses to be awarded for their academic achievements and participation! Save your bucks for Cash Cow’s auction at the end of the semester where you can win big ticket prizes!

Earn them by
💚 Acing your academics
💛 Attending School of Business Events
❤️ Engaging on social media
AND MORE!

Business Bucks expire at the end of each semester.

#ATUBusiness #HeckYeahTechYeah
